N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 1156.10 - Fees

State Regulations

The fee for copies of records not in excess of 9 by 14 inches
is 25 cents per copy. The fee for copies of all other records shall be the
actual cost of reproducing the record, except when a different fee is otherwise
prescribed by statute. Notes
